00:00:31.270 --> 00:00:38.450
Air travel is something that has gone from being a luxury available only to the richest in society

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:44.800
to something that, at least in most parts of the developed world, is available to everyone.

00:00:45.390 --> 00:00:49.120
This all happened over the space of less than 100 years.

00:00:49.370 --> 00:00:53.010
